-- France Will Support Measures to Limit Agricultural Speculation
-- B y   R u d y   R u i t e n b e r g   a n d   H e l e n e   F o u q u e t
-- 2012-07-31T14:14:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-31/france-will-support-measures-to-limit-agricultural-speculation.html
France  would back measures to limit
speculation on agricultural products, Agriculture Minister
Stephane Le Foll said in parliamentary debate today, without
providing details.  “The government will support any action to limit the
speculation on agricultural and animal products,” Le Foll said.  To contact the reporters on this story:
